ZH: 我们今天一定要干活儿，不能拖了。
EN: We must work hard today, we can't delay.

ZH: 这个周末我要好好干活儿，把房间清理干净。
EN: I'll work hard this weekend, clean up the room.

ZH: 他很有干活儿的精神，从早到晚都在忙碌。
EN: He's very diligent, busy from morning till night.

ZH: 别整天玩游戏，应该认真干活儿。
EN: Stop playing games all day, you should work hard.

ZH: 妈妈一直在厨房忙着干活儿，真辛苦。
EN: Mom has been busy working in the kitchen, she's tired.

ZH: 家里很脏，我们得赶紧干活儿。
EN: The house is very dirty, we need to clean up quickly.

ZH: 我每周六都会安排时间干活儿。
EN: I allocate time for housework every Saturday.

ZH: 学生们非常配合，一起干活儿把教室打扫干净。
EN: The students cooperate well, cleaning the classroom together.

ZH: 他对干活儿一点都不感兴趣，总是拖拖拉拉。
EN: He is not interested in working at all, always procrastinating.

ZH: 老板看到大家都在努力干活儿，表示很满意。
EN: The boss is very satisfied to see everyone working hard.

ZH: 每个人都有责任干活儿，不能总是依赖别人。
EN: Everyone has the responsibility to work, can't always rely on others.

ZH: 爸爸每天早上都会鼓励我们起床干活儿。
EN: Dad encourages us to wake up and work every morning.

ZH: 队长负责安排每个队员的干活儿任务。
EN: The captain is responsible for assigning tasks to each team member.

ZH: 老师教育我们要勤奋干活儿，才能取得成绩。
EN: The teacher educates us to work hard in order to achieve results.

ZH: 我们一起动手干活儿，效率更高。
EN: Working together will increase efficiency.

ZH: 秋天到了，我们要干活儿收割庄稼。
EN: Autumn is here, we need to work in the fields to harvest crops.

ZH: 孩子们每周末都会帮忙干活儿，学会自理。
EN: The children help with housework every weekend, learning to take care of themselves.

ZH: 我们家每个人都有分工干活儿的职责。
EN: Everyone in our family has their own responsibilities for housework.

ZH: 大家一起干活儿，就能提高团队合作能力。
EN: Working together will improve teamwork skills.

ZH: 身体健康要靠运动和干活儿来保持。
EN: Healthy body requires exercise and physical work to maintain.
